snippet.title: Space Bob vs. The Replicons (Free PC Game - Updated Trailer)
snippet.description:
Poor Bob. No sooner has he finished his basic training than his A.I. companion detects a Replicon mothership jump signature. This is not the best of news considering all Replicons seemingly have one thing in common: kill all humans!. Download link below the fold.

Help Bob to explore and collect the resources he needs to reach the Jump Gate and escape.

Download and play for free - https://paul-intravenous.itch.io/space-bob-vs-the-replicons

Music used: End Game by Per Kiilstofte
https://machinimasound.com/music/end-game
